race.comment: Competitive. WHITE HOT MAMA (9) was heavily bet at Ballarat stepping up to this trip and was beaten a half length after rolling across to the speed. Will do the same here with Meech booked, and she can go one better with the extra fitness. MAGNETIC CHESS (2) has run the quinella heavily bet both race starts. Led and missed a whisker at Hamilton the latest. Will lead or box seat from an inside gate and is sure to give a sight. SHADES OF STARDOM (4) missed a whisker here first-up and then placed second at the track/trip behind a dominant winner. He will be better for that outing and Yendall will give him every chance.  PRINCE IADORA (3) was doing his best work late when beaten 2.6L at Ballarat on debut. John Allen stays aboard and on the fresh side he also has claims.
